pan class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fdn1665702523449.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fdn1665702523449.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fdn1665702523449.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fdn1665702523449\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fdn1665702523449___log_274199\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the base 10 logarithm of X (log<sub class=\"ph sub\">10</sub>X). </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__topic_d85814e1_d85815e1_d85816e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__p_d85817e1_d85818e1_d85819e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$log10</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__topic_d57037e1_d57038e1_d57039e1_d57040e1_d57041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d958330e77\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__d7174e20\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>— positive numeric constant, or a\n        field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates\n        to a positive numeric value. <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var> must be in the range 0 through\n          10<sup class=\"ph sup\">9999</sup>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__topic_d57042e1_d57043e1_d57044e1_d57045e1_d57046e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d958330e94\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__p_d85829e1_d85830e1_d85831e1\">Base 10 logarithm of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__p_d85832e1_d85833e1_d85834e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$log</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$log10</span>.</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> -1204 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_NEGATIVE&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Negative value not allowed. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\"> -1205 </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ZERO&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"fdn1665702523449__table_d9062e1_d9063e1_d9064e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Zero value not allowed. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__topic_d57047e1_d57048e1_d57049e1_d57050e1_d57051e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d958330e202\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__topic_d57052e1_d57053e1_d57054e1_d57055e1_d57056e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d958330e212\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__p_d85844e1_d85845e1_d85846e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$log10</span> returns the\n            base 10 logarithm of <var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>, that is, log<sub class=\"ph sub\">10</sub>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">X</var>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__section_spt_j5b_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d958330e233\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$log10</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following example returns the base 10 logarithm of the given\n               expression:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"fdn1665702523449__pre_amf_k5b_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$NOTNATLOG$ = $log10(MYFIELD * 2)\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">If the value of MYFIELD is 50, the value stored in $NOTNATLOG$ is\n               2.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tsb1719651708881.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$log</a><p>Return the natural logarithm of X (log e X).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/boh1719653049340.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$exp10</a><p>Return the base 10 exponential of X (10X).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527456\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$log10 Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the base 10 logarithm of X (log 10 X). $log10 ( X ) Parameters X — positive numeric constant, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), variable, function, or expression that evaluates to a positive numeric value. X must be in the range 0 through 10 9999 . Return Values Base 10 logarithm of X If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 1. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $log and $log10 . Value Error constant Meaning -1204 <UPROCERR_NEGATIVE> Negative value not allowed. -1205 <UPROCERR_ZERO> Zero value not allowed. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The function $log10 returns the base 10 logarithm of X , that is, log 10 X . Example: Using $log10 The following example returns the base 10 logarithm of the given expression: $NOTNATLOG$ = $log10(MYFIELD * 2) Copy If the value of MYFIELD is 50, the value stored in $NOTNATLOG$ is 2. Related Links $log Return the natural logarithm of X (log e X). $exp10 Return the base 10 exponential of X (10X). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}